"1115","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0>&nbsp;</P>"
"1116","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0>Dear Sirs:</P>"
"1117","<P STYLE=font: 14pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0>&nbsp;</P>"
"1118","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>This Interim Management"
"1119","Agreement (this &ldquo;Agreement&rdquo;), dated as of March 25, 2019, is by and between the James Advantage Funds (the &ldquo;Trust&rdquo;),"
"1120","on behalf of the James Aggressive Allocation Fund (the &ldquo;Fund&rdquo;) and James Investment Research, Inc. (the &ldquo;Adviser&rdquo;)"
"1121","(each a &ldquo;Party&rdquo; and collectively, the &ldquo;Parties&rdquo;).</P>"
"1122","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>&nbsp;</P>"
"1123","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>WHEREAS, the Adviser and"
"1124","the Trust entered into a Management Agreement dated July 1, 2015 (the &ldquo;Advisory Agreement&rdquo;); and</P>"
"1125","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>&nbsp;</P>"
"1126","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>WHEREAS, the Advisory Agreement"
"1127","between the Trust, on behalf of the Fund, and the Adviser has been terminated by the assignment of the Advisory Agreement;</P>"
"1128","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>&nbsp;</P>"
"1129","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>WHEREAS, Rule 15a-4 under"
"1130","the 1940 Act (&ldquo;Rule 15a-4&rdquo;) permits an interim investment advisory agreement subject to and in conformity the terms"
"1131","of such rule; and</P>"
"1132","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>&nbsp;</P>"
"1133","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>WHEREAS, the Trust seeks"
"1134","to retain the Adviser, pursuant to Rule 15a-4, to furnish investment advisory and other services to the Trust for the Fund;</P>"
"1135","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>&nbsp;</P>"
"1136","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>NOW, THEREFORE, in consideration"
"1137","of the mutual covenants and agreements contained in this Agreement and for other good and valuable consideration, the receipt and"
"1138","adequacy of which are hereby acknowledged, the Adviser and the Trust agree as follows:</P>"
"1139","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>&nbsp;</P>"
"1140","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0>The James Advantage Funds (The Trust) herewith confirms our agreement"
"1141","with you.</P>"
"1142","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0>&nbsp;</P>"
"1143","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>The Trust has been"
"1144","organized to engage in the business of an investment company. The Trust currently offers several series of shares to"
"1145","investors, one of which is the James Aggressive Allocation Fund (the &ldquo;Fund&rdquo;).</P>"
"1146","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify>&nbsp;</P>"
"1147","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>You have been selected"
"1148","to act as the sole investment adviser of the Fund and to provide certain other services, as more fully set forth below, and you"
"1149","are willing to act as such investment adviser and to perform such services under the terms and conditions hereinafter set forth."
"1150","Accordingly, the Trust agrees with you as follows upon the date of execution of this Agreement.</P>"
"1151","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify>&nbsp;</P>"
"1152","<TABLE CELLPADDING=0 CELLSPACING=0 WIDTH=100% STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0><TR STYLE=vertical-align: top>"
"1153","<TD STYLE=width: 0.5in></TD><TD STYLE=width: 0.25in>1.</TD><TD STYLE=text-align: justify><U>ADVISORY SERVICES</U></TD></TR></TABLE>"
"1154","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0 0 0 0.75in; text-align: justify>&nbsp;</P>"
"1155","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>You will regularly provide"
"1156","the Fund with such investment advice as you in your discretion deem advisable and will furnish a continuous investment program"
"1157","for the Fund consistent with the Fund&rsquo;s investment objectives and policies. You will determine the securities to be purchased"
"1158","for the Fund, the portfolio securities to be held or sold by the Fund and the portion of the Fund&rsquo;s assets to be held uninvested,"
"1159","subject always to the fund&rsquo;s investment objectives, policies and restrictions, as each of the same shall be from time to"
"1160","time in effect, and subject further to such policies and instructions as the Board of Trustees (the &ldquo;Board&rdquo;) may from"
"1161","time to time establish. You will advise and assist the officers of the Trust in taking such steps as are necessary or appropriate"
"1162","to carry out the decisions of the Board and the appropriate committees of the Board regarding the conduct of the business of the"
"1163","Fund.</P>"
"1164","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>&nbsp;</P>"
"1165","<!-- Field: Page; Sequence: 1 -->"
"1166","    <DIV STYLE=margin-bottom: 6pt><P STYLE=margin: 0pt; font: 9pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif>&nbsp;</P></DIV>"
"1167","    <DIV STYLE=page-break-before: always; margin-top: 6pt><P STYLE=margin: 0pt>&nbsp;</P></DIV>"
"1168","    <!-- Field: /Page -->"
"1169","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify></P>"
"1170","<TABLE CELLPADDING=0 CELLSPACING=0 WIDTH=100% STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0><TR STYLE=vertical-align: top>"
"1171","<TD STYLE=width: 0.5in></TD><TD STYLE=width: 0.25in>2.</TD><TD STYLE=text-align: justify><U>ALLOCATION OF CHARGES AND EXPENSES</U></TD></TR></TABLE>"
"1172","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify>&nbsp;</P>"
"1173","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>You will pay all organizational,"
"1174","offering and operating expenses (other than expenses specifically assumed by the Fund) of the Fund, including the compensation"
"1175","and expenses of any employees of the Fund and of any other persons rendering any services to the Fund; clerical and shareholder"
"1176","service staff salaries; office space and other office expenses; fees and expenses incurred by the Fund in connection with membership"
"1177","in investment company organizations; legal, auditing and accounting expenses; expenses of registering shares under federal and"
"1178","state securities laws; insurance expenses; fees and expenses of the custodian, transfer agent, dividend and dispersing agent, shareholder"
"1179","service agent, plan agent, administrator, accounting and pricing services agent and underwriter of the Fund; expenses, including"
"1180","clerical expenses, of issue, sale redemption or repurchase of shares of the Fund; the cost of preparing and distributing reports"
"1181","and notices to shareholders, the cost of printing or preparing prospectuses and statements</P>"
"1182","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify>&nbsp;</P>"
"1183","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify>of additional information for delivery to the"
"1184","Fund&rsquo;s current shareholders; the cost of printing or preparing stock certificates or any other documents, statements or reports"
"1185","to shareholders; expenses of shareholders&rsquo; meetings and proxy solicitations; and all other operating expenses not specifically"
"1186","assumed by the Fund.</P>"
"1187","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify>&nbsp;</P>"
"1188","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>The Fund will pay the brokerage"
"1189","fees and commissions, taxes, interest, fees and expenses of the non-interested person trustees and such extraordinary or non-recurring"
"1190","expenses as may arise, including litigation to which the Fund may be a party and indemnification of the Trust&rsquo;s trustees"
"1191","and officers with respect thereto. The Fund will pay all expenses, if any, which may be incurred pursuant to the Fund&rsquo;s Rule"
"1192","12b-1 Distribution Plan (the &ldquo;12b-1 Expenses&rdquo;). You may obtain reimbursement from the Fund, at such time or times as"
"1193","you may determine in your sole discretion, for any of the expenses advanced by you, which the Fund is obligated to pay, and such"
"1194","reimbursement shall not be considered to be part of your compensation pursuant to this Agreement.</P>"
"1195","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify>&nbsp;</P>"
"1196","<TABLE CELLPADDING=0 CELLSPACING=0 WIDTH=100% STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0><TR STYLE=vertical-align: top>"
"1197","<TD STYLE=width: 0.5in></TD><TD STYLE=width: 0.25in>3.</TD><TD STYLE=text-align: justify><U>COMPENSATION OF THE ADVISER</U></TD></TR></TABLE>"
"1198","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify>&nbsp;</P>"
"1199","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>For all services to be"
"1200","rendered and payments to be made as provided in this Agreement, as of the last business day of each month, the Fund will pay you"
"1201","a fee: (a) at the annual rate of 0.98% of the average value of its net daily assets for assets up to and including $500 million,"
"1202","(b) at an annual rate of 0.95% of the average value of its daily net assets from $500 million up to and including $1 billion, (c)"
"1203","at an annual rate of 0.90% of the average daily net assets up to and including $2 billion, and at an annual rate of 0.85% of the"
"1204","average value of its daily net assets over $2 billion.</P>"
"1205","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>&nbsp;</P>"
"1206","<!-- Field: Page; Sequence: 2 -->"
"1207","    <DIV STYLE=margin-bottom: 6pt><P STYLE=margin: 0pt; font: 9pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif>&nbsp;</P></DIV>"
"1208","    <DIV STYLE=page-break-before: always; margin-top: 6pt><P STYLE=margin: 0pt>&nbsp;</P></DIV>"
"1209","    <!-- Field: /Page -->"
"1210","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify></P>"
"1211","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>The average value of the"
"1212","daily net assets of the Fund shall be determined pursuant to the applicable provisions of the Declaration of Trust or a resolution"
"1213","of the Board, if required. If, pursuant to such provisions, the determination of net asset value of the Fund is suspended for any"
"1214","particular business day, then for the purpose of this paragraph, the value of the net assets of the Fund as last determined shall"
"1215","be deemed to be the value of the net assets as of the close of the business day, or as of such other time as the value of the Fund&rsquo;s"
"1216","net assets may lawfully be determined, on that day. If the determination of the net asset value of the Fund has been suspended"
"1217","for a period including such month, your compensation payable at the end of such month shall be computed on the basis of the value"
"1218","of the net assets of the Fund as last determined (whether during or prior to such month).</P>"
"1219","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>&nbsp;</P>"
"1220","<TABLE CELLPADDING=0 CELLSPACING=0 WIDTH=100% STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0><TR STYLE=vertical-align: top>"
"1221","<TD STYLE=width: 0.5in></TD><TD STYLE=width: 0.25in>4.</TD><TD STYLE=text-align: justify><U>EXECUTION OF PURCHASE AND SALE ORDERS</U></TD></TR></TABLE>"
"1222","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify>&nbsp;</P>"
"1223","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>In connection with purchases"
"1224","or sales of portfolio securities for the account of the Fund, it is understood that you will arrange for the placing of all orders"
"1225","for the purchase and sale of portfolio securities for the account with brokers or dealers selected by you, subject to review of"
"1226","this selection by the Board from time to time. You will be responsible for the negotiation and the allocation of principal business"
"1227","and portfolio brokerage. In the selection of such brokers or dealers and the placing of such orders, you are directed at all times"
"1228","to seek for the Fund the best qualitative execution, taking into account such factors as prices (including the applicable brokerage"
"1229","commission or dealer spread) the execution capability, financial responsibility and responsiveness of the broker or dealer and"
"1230","the brokerage and research services provided by the broker or dealer.</P>"
"1231","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify>&nbsp;</P>"
"1232","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>You should generally seek"
"1233","favorable prices and commission rates that are reasonable in relation to the benefits received. In seeking the best qualified execution,"
"1234","you are authorized to select brokers or dealers who also provide brokerage and research services (as those terms are defined in"
"1235","Section 28(e) of the Securities Exchange Act of 1934) to the Fund and/or the other accounts over which you exercise investment"
"1236","discretion. You are authorized to pay a broker or dealer who provides such brokerage and research services a commission for executing"
"1237","a Fund portfolio transaction which is in excess of the amount of the commission another broker or dealer would have charged for"
"1238","effecting that transaction if you determine in good faith that the amount of the commission is reasonable in relation to the value"
"1239","of the brokerage and research services provided by the executing broker or dealer. The determination may be viewed in terms of"
"1240","either a particular transaction or your overall responsibilities with respect to the Fund and acknowledge that, although the information"
"1241","may be useful to the Fund and you, it is not possible to place a dollar value on such information. The Board shall periodically"
"1242","review the commissions paid by the Fund to determine if the commissions paid over representative periods of time were reasonable"
"1243","in relation to the benefits to the Fund.</P>"
"1244","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>&nbsp;</P>"
"1245","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>Subject to the provisions"
"1246","of the Investment Company Act of 1940, as amended (The &ldquo;Act&rdquo;) and other applicable law, you, any of you affiliates"
"1247","or affiliates of your affiliates may retain compensation in connection with effecting the Fund&rsquo;s portfolio transactions,"
"1248","including transactions effected through others. If any occasions should arise in which you give any advice to clients of yours"
"1249","concerning the shares of the fund, you will act solely as investment counsel for such client and not in any way on behalf of the"
"1250","Fund. Your services to the Fund, pursuant to the Agreement are not to be deemed to be exclusive and it is understood that you may"
"1251","render investment advice, management and other services to others, including other registered investment companies.</P>"
"1252","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>&nbsp;</P>"
