"1259","<TD STYLE=width: 0.5in></TD><TD STYLE=width: 0.25in>5.</TD><TD STYLE=text-align: justify><U>LIMITATION OF LIABILITY OF ADVISER</U></TD></TR></TABLE>"
"1260","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify>&nbsp;</P>"
"1261","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>You may rely on information"
"1262","reasonably believed by you to be accurate and reliable. Except as otherwise may be required by the Act or the rules thereunder,"
"1263","neither you nor your officers, directors, employees, agents control persons or affiliates of any thereof shall be subject to any"
"1264","liability, for any damages, expenses or losses incurred by the Trust in connection with, any error of judgment, mistake of law,"
"1265","any act or omission connected with or arising out of and services rendered under, or payments made pursuant to, this Agreement"
"1266","or any other matter to which the Agreement relates, except by reason of willful misfeasance, bad faith or gross negligence on the"
"1267","part of any such persons in the performance of your duties under this Agreement, or by reason of reckless disregard by any of such"
"1268","persons of your obligations and duties under this Agreement.</P>"
"1269","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify>&nbsp;</P>"
"1270","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>Any person, even though"
"1271","also a director, officer, employee or agent of you, who may be or may become an officer, director, trustee, employee or agent of"
"1272","the Trust, shall be deemed, when rendering services to the Trust or acting on any business of the Trust (other than services or"
"1273","business in connection with you duties hereunder), to be rendering such services to or acting solely for the Trust and not as a"
"1274","director, officer, employees or agent of you, or one under your control or direction, even though paid by you.</P>"
"1275","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify>&nbsp;</P>"
"1276","<TABLE CELLPADDING=0 CELLSPACING=0 WIDTH=100% STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0><TR STYLE=vertical-align: top>"
"1277","<TD STYLE=width: 0.5in></TD><TD STYLE=width: 0.25in>6.</TD><TD STYLE=text-align: justify><U>DURATION AND TERMINATION OF THIS AGREEMENT</U></TD></TR></TABLE>"
"1278","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify>&nbsp;</P>"
"1279","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>This Agreement shall take"
"1280","effect on the date of its execution by you, and shall remain in force for a period of one hundred and fifty (150) days years from"
"1281","the date of its execution.</P>"
"1282","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>&nbsp;</P>"
"1283","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>This Agreement may, on"
"1284","ten (10) days written notice, be terminated with respect to the Fund, at any time without the payment of any penalty, by the Board"
"1285","or by a vote of a majority of the outstanding voting securities of the Fund. This Agreement may also be terminated by you on sixty"
"1286","(60) days&rsquo; prior written notice to the Trust. The Agreement shall automatically terminate in the event of its assignment.</P>"
"1287","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify>&nbsp;</P>"
"1288","<TABLE CELLPADDING=0 CELLSPACING=0 WIDTH=100% STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0><TR STYLE=vertical-align: top>"
"1289","<TD STYLE=width: 0.5in></TD><TD STYLE=width: 0.25in>7.</TD><TD STYLE=text-align: justify><U>USE OF NAME</U></TD></TR></TABLE>"
"1290","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify>&nbsp;</P>"
"1291","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>The Trust and you acknowledge"
"1292","that all rights to the name &ldquo;James Aggressive Allocation Fund&rdquo; or any variation thereof, belongs to you, and that the"
"1293","Trust is being granted a limited license to use such words in its Fund name or in any class name. In the event you cease to be"
"1294","the adviser to the Fund, the Trust&rsquo;s right to use the name &ldquo;James Aggressive Allocation Fund&rdquo; or any variation"
"1295","thereof, shall automatically cease on the ninetieth (90<SUP>th</SUP>) day following the termination of the Agreement. The right"
"1296","to the name may also be withdrawn by you during the term of this Agreement upon ninety (90) days written notice by you to the Trust."
"1297","Nothing contained herein shall impair or diminish in any respect, your right to use the name &ldquo;James Aggressive Allocation"
"1298","Fund&rdquo;, or any variation thereof, in the name of, or in connection with, any other business enterprise with which you are"
"1299","or may become associated. There is no charge to the Trust for the right to use these names.</P>"
