"1310","may be changed, waived, discharges or terminated orally, and no amendment of the Agreement shall be effective until approved by"
"1311","the Board, including a majority of the Trustees who are not interested persons of you or of the Trust, cast in person at a meeting"
"1312","called for the purpose of voting on such approval, and (if required under interpretations of the Act by the Securities and Exchange"
"1313","Commission) by a vote of the holders of a majority of the outstanding voting securities of the series to which the amendment relates.</P>"
"1314","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>&nbsp;</P>"
"1315","<TABLE CELLPADDING=0 CELLSPACING=0 WIDTH=100% STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0><TR STYLE=vertical-align: top>"
"1316","<TD STYLE=width: 0.5in></TD><TD STYLE=width: 0.25in>9.</TD><TD STYLE=text-align: justify><U>LIMITATION OF LIABILITY TO TRUST PROPERTY</U></TD></TR></TABLE>"
"1317","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify>&nbsp;</P>"
"1318","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>The term &ldquo;James Advantage"
"1319","Funds&rdquo; means and refers to the Trustees from time to time serving under the Trust&rsquo;s Declaration of Trust as the same"
"1320","may subsequently thereto have been, or subsequently hereto be, amended. It is expressly agreed that the obligations of the Trust"
"1321","hereunder shall not be binding upon any of the Trustees, shareholders, nominees, officers, agents or employees of the Trust personally,"
"1322","but bind only the Trust property of the Trust, as provided in the Declaration of the Trust. The execution and delivery of this"
"1323","Agreement have been authorized by the Trustees and shareholders of the Trust and signed by officers of the Trust, acting as such,"
"1324","and neither such authorization by such Trustees and shareholders nor such execution and delivery by such officers shall be deemed"
"1325","to have been made by any of them individually or to impose any liability on any of them personally, but shall bind only the Trust"
"1326","property of the Trust as provided by the Declaration of Trust. A copy of the Agreement and Declaration of Trust of the Trusts is"
"1327","on file with the Secretary of the State of Ohio.</P>"
