"1374","their construction or effect.</P>"
"1375","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>&nbsp;</P>"
"1376","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>If you are in agreement"
"1377","with the foregoing, please sign the form of acceptance on the accompanying counterpart of this letter and return such counterpart"
"1378","to the Trust, whereupon this letter shall become a binding contract upon the date thereof.</P>"
"1379","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>&nbsp;</P>"
