"1967","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>If the shareholders of"
"1968","the Fund fail to approve the Agreement in the manner set forth above, upon request of the Board, you will continue to serve or"
"1969","act in such capacity for the Fund for the period of time pending required approval of the Agreement, of a new agreement with you"
"1970","or a different adviser or other definitive action; provided that the compensation to be paid by the Fund to you for your services"
"1971","to and payments on behalf of the Fund will be equal to the lesser of your actual costs incurred in furnishing such services and"
"1972","payments or the amount you would have received under this Agreement for furnishing such services and payments.</P>"
"1973","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>&nbsp;</P>"
"1974","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>This Agreement may, on"
"1975","sixty days written notice, be terminated with respect to the Fund, at any time without the payment of any penalty, by the Board,"
"1976","by a vote of a majority of the outstanding voting securities of the Fund, or by you. This Agreement shall automatically terminate"
"1977","in the event of its assignment.</P>"
"1978","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>&nbsp;</P>"
