"1983","that all rights to the name &ldquo;James Small Cap,&rdquo; or any variation thereof, belongs to you, and that the Trust is being"
"1984","granted a limited license to use such words in its Fund name or in any class name. In the event you cease to be the adviser to"
"1985","the Fund, the Trust&rsquo;s right to use of the name&rdquo; James Small Cap, or any variation thereof, shall automatically cease"
"1986","on the ninetieth day following the termination of this Agreement. The right to the name may also be withdrawn by you during the"
"1987","term of this Agreement upon ninety (90) days&rsquo; written notice by you to the Trust. Nothing contained herein shall impair or"
"1988","diminish in any respect, your right to use the name &ldquo;James Small Cap,&rdquo; or any variation thereof, in the name of, or"
"1989","in connection with, any other business enterprises with which you are or may become associated. There is no charge to the Trust"
"1990","for the right to use these names.</P>"
