"1996","may be changed, waived, discharged or terminated orally, and no amendment of this Agreement shall be effective until approved by"
"1997","the Board, including a majority of the trustees who are not interested persons of you or of the Trust, cast in person at a meeting"
"1998","called for the purpose of voting on such approval, and (if required under interpretations of the Act by the Securities and Exchange"
"1999","Commission) by vote of the holders of a majority of the outstanding voting securities of the series to which the amendment relates.</P>"
"2000","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>&nbsp;</P>"
"2001","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-transform: uppercase; text-indent: 0.5in><FONT STYLE=text-transform: none>9.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</FONT><U>LIMITATION"
"2002","OF LIABILITY TO TRUST PROPERTY</U></P>"
"2003","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-transform: uppercase; text-indent: 0.5in><FONT STYLE=text-decoration: none>&nbsp;</FONT></P>"
"2004","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>The term &ldquo;The James"
"2005","Advantage Funds&rdquo; means and refers to the Trustees from time to time serving under the Trust&rsquo;s Declaration of Trust"
"2006","as the same may subsequently thereto have been, or subsequently hereto be, amended. It is expressly agreed that the obligations"
"2007","of the Trust hereunder shall not be binding upon any of the trustees, shareholders, nominees, officers, agents or employees of"
"2008","the Trust personally, but bind only the trust property of the Trust, as provided in the Declaration of Trust of the Trust. The"
"2009","execution and delivery of this Agreement have been authorized by the trustees and shareholders of the Trust and signed by officers"
"2010","of the Trust, acting as such, and neither such authorization by such trustees and shareholders nor such execution and delivery"
"2011","by such officers shall be deemed to have been made by any of them individually or to impose any liability on any of them personally,"
"2012","but shall bind only the trust property of the Trust as provided in its Declaration of Trust. A copy of the Agreement and Declaration"
"2013","of Trust of the Trust is on file with the Secretary of the State of Ohio.</P>"
