"2724","of this Agreement is determined to be void or unenforceable, such determination shall not affect the remainder of this Agreement,"
"2725","which shall continue to be in force.</P>"
"2726","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>&nbsp;</P>"
