"2745","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-indent: 0.5in>13.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<FONT STYLE=font-family: Times New Roman, Times, Serif; font-size: 11pt><U>COUNTERPARTS</U></FONT></P>"
"2746","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-indent: 0.5in><FONT STYLE=text-decoration: none>&nbsp;</FONT></P>"
"2747","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>This Agreement may be executed"
"2748","in one or more counterparts, each of which shall be deemed an original, but all of which together shall constitute one and the"
"2749","same instrument.</P>"
"2750","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>&nbsp;</P>"
"2751","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-indent: 0.5in>14.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<FONT STYLE=font-family: Times New Roman, Times, Serif; font-size: 11pt><U>BINDING"
"2752","EFFECT</U></FONT></P>"
"2753","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-indent: 0.5in><FONT STYLE=text-decoration: none>&nbsp;</FONT></P>"
"2754","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>Each of the undersigned"
"2755","expressly warrants and represents that he has the full power and authority to sign this Agreement on behalf of the party indicated,"
"2756","and that his signature will operate to bind the party indicated to the foregoing terms.</P>"
"2757","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>&nbsp;</P>"
"2758","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-indent: 0.5in>15.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<FONT STYLE=font-family: Times New Roman, Times, Serif; font-size: 11pt><U>CAPTIONS</U></FONT></P>"
"2759","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-indent: 0.5in><FONT STYLE=text-decoration: none>&nbsp;</FONT></P>"
"2760","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>The captions in this Agreement"
"2761","are included for convenience of reference only and in no way define or delimit any of the provisions hereof or otherwise affect"
"2762","their construction or effect.</P>"
"2763","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>&nbsp;</P>"
"2764","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>If you are in agreement"
"2765","with the foregoing, please sign the form of acceptance on the accompanying counterpart of this letter and return such counterpart"
"2766","to the Trust, whereupon this letter shall become a binding contract upon the date thereof.</P>"
"2767","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>&nbsp;</P>"
