"3015","<TD STYLE=width: 0.5in></TD><TD STYLE=width: 0.25in>7.</TD><TD STYLE=text-align: justify><U>USE OF NAME</U></TD></TR></TABLE>"
"3016","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify>&nbsp;</P>"
"3017","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>The Trust and you acknowledge"
"3018","that all rights to the name &ldquo;James Aggressive Allocation Fund&rdquo; or any variation thereof, belongs to you, and that the"
"3019","Trust is being granted a limited license to use such words in its Fund name or in any class name. In the event you cease to be"
"3020","the adviser to the Fund, the Trust&rsquo;s right to use the name &ldquo;James Aggressive Allocation Fund&rdquo; or any variation"
"3021","thereof, shall automatically cease on the ninetieth (90<SUP>th</SUP>) day following the termination of the Agreement. The right"
"3022","to the name may also be withdrawn by you during the term of this Agreement upon ninety (90) days written notice by you to the Trust."
"3023","Nothing contained herein shall impair or diminish in any respect, your right to use the name &ldquo;James Aggressive Allocation"
"3024","Fund&rdquo;, or any variation thereof, in the name of, or in connection with, any other business enterprise with which you are"
"3025","or may become associated. There is no charge to the Trust for the right to use these names.</P>"
