"3046","may subsequently thereto have been, or subsequently hereto be, amended. It is expressly agreed that the obligations of the Trust"
"3047","hereunder shall not be binding upon any of the Trustees, shareholders, nominees, officers, agents or employees of the Trust personally,"
"3048","but bind only the Trust property of the Trust, as provided in the Declaration of the Trust. The execution and delivery of this"
"3049","Agreement have been authorized by the Trustees and shareholders of the Trust and signed by officers of the Trust, acting as such,"
"3050","and neither such authorization by such Trustees and shareholders nor such execution and delivery by such officers shall be deemed"
"3051","to have been made by any of them individually or to impose any liability on any of them personally, but shall bind only the Trust"
"3052","property of the Trust as provided by the Declaration of Trust. A copy of the Agreement and Declaration of Trust of the Trusts is"
"3053","on file with the Secretary of the State of Ohio.</P>"
