"3428","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0 0 0 1in; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0in>&nbsp;</P>"
"3429","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-indent: 0.5in>12.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<U>NOTICES</U></P>"
"3430","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-indent: 0.5in>&nbsp;</P>"
"3431","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>Any notices under this"
"3432","Agreement shall be in writing, addressed and delivered or mailed postage paid to the other party at such address as such other"
"3433","party may designate for the receipt of such notice. Until further notice to the other party, it is agreed that the address of the"
"3434","Trust is 1290 Broadway, Suite 1100, Denver, CO 80203, and your address for this purpose shall be P.O. Box 8, Alpha, Ohio 45301.</P>"
"3435","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>&nbsp;</P>"
"3436","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-indent: 0.5in>13.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<U>COUNTERPARTS</U></P>"
"3437","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-indent: 0.5in>&nbsp;</P>"
"3438","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>This Agreement may be executed"
"3439","in one or more counterparts, each of which shall be deemed an original, but all of which together shall constitute one and the"
"3440","same instrument.</P>"
"3441","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>&nbsp;</P>"
"3442","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-indent: 0.5in>14.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<U>BINDING"
"3443","EFFECT</U></P>"
"3444","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-indent: 0.5in>&nbsp;</P>"
