"3446","expressly warrants and represents that he has the full power and authority to sign this Agreement on behalf of the party indicated,"
"3447","and that his signature will operate to bind the party indicated to the foregoing terms.</P>"
"3448","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>&nbsp;</P>"
