"3700","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify></P>"
"3701","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>Any person, even though"
"3702","also a director, officer, employee or agent of you, who may be or become an officer, director, trustee, employee or agent of the"
"3703","Trust, shall be deemed, when rendering services to the Trust or acting on any business of the Trust (other than services or business"
"3704","in connection with your duties hereunder), to be rendering such services to or acting solely for the Trust and not as a director,"
"3705","officer, employee or agent of you, or one under your control or direction, even though paid by you.</P>"
"3706","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>&nbsp;</P>"
"3707","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-transform: uppercase; text-indent: 0.5in><FONT STYLE=text-transform: none>6.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</FONT><U>DURATION"
"3708","AND TERMINATION OF THIS AGREEMENT</U></P>"
"3709","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-transform: uppercase; text-indent: 0.5in><FONT STYLE=text-decoration: none>&nbsp;</FONT></P>"
"3710","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>This Agreement shall take"
"3711","effect on the date of its execution by you, and shall remain in force for a period of one hundred and fifty (150) days from the"
"3712","date of its execution.</P>"
"3713","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>&nbsp;</P>"
"3714","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>This Agreement may, on"
"3715","ten days written notice, be terminated with respect to the Fund, at any time without the payment of any penalty, by the Board or"
"3716","by a vote of a majority of the outstanding voting securities of the Fund. This Agreement may also be terminated by you on sixty"
"3717","days&rsquo; prior written notice to the Trust. This Agreement shall automatically terminate in the event of its assignment.</P>"
"3718","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>&nbsp;</P>"
"3719","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-transform: uppercase; text-indent: 0.5in><FONT STYLE=text-transform: none>7.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</FONT><U>USE"
"3720","oF NAME</U></P>"
"3721","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-transform: uppercase; text-indent: 0.5in><FONT STYLE=text-decoration: none>&nbsp;</FONT></P>"
"3722","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>The Trust and you acknowledge"
"3723","that all rights to the name &ldquo;James Small Cap,&rdquo; or any variation thereof, belongs to you, and that the Trust is being"
"3724","granted a limited license to use such words in its Fund name or in any class name. In the event you cease to be the adviser to"
"3725","the Fund, the Trust&rsquo;s right to use of the name&rdquo; James Small Cap, or any variation thereof, shall automatically cease"
"3726","on the ninetieth day following the termination of this Agreement. The right to the name may also be withdrawn by you during the"
"3727","term of this Agreement upon ninety (90) days&rsquo; written notice by you to the Trust. Nothing contained herein shall impair or"
"3728","diminish in any respect, your right to use the name &ldquo;James Small Cap,&rdquo; or any variation thereof, in the name of, or"
"3729","in connection with, any other business enterprises with which you are or may become associated. There is no charge to the Trust"
"3730","for the right to use these names.</P>"
"3731","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>&nbsp;</P>"
