"3736","may be changed, waived, discharged or terminated orally, and no amendment of this Agreement shall be effective until approved by"
"3737","the Board, including a majority of the trustees who are not interested persons of you or of the Trust, cast in person at a meeting"
"3738","called for the purpose of voting on such approval, and (if required under interpretations of the Act by the Securities and Exchange"
"3739","Commission) by vote of the holders of a majority of the outstanding voting securities of the series to which the amendment relates.</P>"
"3740","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>&nbsp;</P>"
