"4118","party may designate for the receipt of such notice. Until further notice to the other party, it is agreed that the address of the"
"4119","Trust is 1290 Broadway, Suite 1100, Denver, CO 80203, and your address for this purpose shall be P.O. Box 8, Alpha, Ohio 45301.</P>"
