"4125","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify></P>"
"4126","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>13.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<U>COUNTERPARTS</U></P>"
"4127","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>&nbsp;</P>"
"4128","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 84px>&#9;This Agreement may"
"4129","be executed in one or more counterparts, each of which shall be deemed an original, but all of which together shall constitute"
"4130","one and the same instrument.</P>"
"4131","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>&nbsp;</P>"
"4132","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>14.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<U>BINDING"
"4133","EFFECT</U></P>"
"4134","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>&nbsp;</P>"
