"4136","expressly warrants and represents that he has the full power and authority to sign this Agreement on behalf of the party indicated,"
"4137","and that his signature will operate to bind the party indicated to the foregoing terms.</P>"
"4138","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>&nbsp;</P>"
"4139","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>15.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<U>CAPTIONS</U></P>"
"4140","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.5in>&nbsp;</P>"
"4141","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify; text-indent: 84px>&#9;The captions in this"
"4142","Agreement are included for convenience of reference only and in no way define or delimit any of the provisions hereof or otherwise"
"4143","affect their construction or effect.</P>"
